headline: GE Aerospace Receives T700 Engine Order for Poland's Apache Guardian Helicopters
summary: GE Aerospace (NYSE:GE) received an order for 210 T700 engines to power the 96 Boeing AH-64E Apache Guardian helicopters for the Polish Armed Forces.
